varsha: Varsha (DVD authoring tool)
varsha:
varsha: Varsha is a GUI based DVD authoring tool for Linux. You can make DVDs
varsha: from your mpeg files as well as digital still pictures (Slideshow
varsha: DVD). You can even combine slideshows with regular video and make
varsha: them accessible through menus. Using Varsha, you can also create
varsha: menus incorporating backdrop of still pictures as well as moving
varsha: video background.
varsha: http://varsha.sourceforge.net/
